snippet.title: Final Fantasy XV: A New Empire - Alexis Ren in "Epic"
snippet.description: Be the hero of your own Final Fantasy adventure in the brand new mobile strategy game Final Fantasy XV: A New Empire! Build your own kingdom, discover powerful magic, and dominate the realm alongside all of your friends!
